Soooooo you're telling me the patcher started to "unpatch"?!

If the percentage jumped back down to a certain point then started working back up, it might be an issue with your OS's permissions. Follow the steps in our [**permission guide**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions) and let me know if that helped!
